:''See also'' [[Wink]]

==English==

===Verb===
'''to wink''' [[intransitive]]
#To [[blink]] with only one [[eye]] as a [[message]], [[signal]], or [[suggestion]]
#To [[twinkle]]
'''to wink''' [[transitive]]
#To send a message etc by winking
===Noun===
'''wink'''
#An act of winking, or a message etc sent by winking
#A [[brief]] [[time]]; an [[instant]]
#A twinkle
#A brief [[period]] of [[sleep]]; especially [[forty winks]]
====Translations====
*French: clin d'oeil (1)
*Lithuanian: sumirkseti

